# Codex authenticates via your local ChatGPT login.
# Run `codex login` on the host (or use the Codex desktop app) before starting Sandcastle.
# The orchestrator mounts ~/.codex into the sandbox — no OPENAI_API_KEY needed.
#
# GitHub: main.mts runs `gh auth token` on the host (using your `gh auth login`
# session) and injects the result into the Docker sandbox as GH_TOKEN.
# Set this only to override that behavior.
GH_TOKEN=
